title: Karchawang
text: Karchawang is a <a href="Village%20development%20committee%20%28Nepal%29">village development committee</a> in <a href="Rolpa%20District">Rolpa District</a> in the <a href="Rapti%20Zone">Rapti Zone</a> of north-eastern <a href="Nepal">Nepal</a>. At the time of the <a href="1991%20Nepal%20census">1991 Nepal census</a> it had a population of 2874 people living in 566 individual households.
